<br>
My equipment:<br>
<br>
Head - Deepwater<br>
Ears - Diamondine and Cougar Claw<br>
Neck - Spider Fur<br>
Shoulders - Crested Spaulders<br>
Face - Seblite Scale<br>
Arms - Deepwater<br>
Bracers - 2 Deepwater<br>
Hands - Silver Chitin Handwraps<br>
Fingers - 6ac 65hp rings<br>
Chest - Enameled Black Chestplate (I hate leather look, which is why I havn't gotten a treeweave)<br>
Waist - Smiters Girdle<br>
Back - Spider Fur<br>
Legs - Greaves of Ro<br>
Feet - Royal Etched Velium (not sure if that is proper name, they are 19ac with  5vs magic and fire or cold)<br>
Range - Eye of Trust (very nice quest item some of you might want to check out http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7611)<br>
Shield - Sarnak Battleshield<br>
1hs - Sword of the Morning<br>
2hs - Abatoirs Combine Greatsword<br>
2hpierceing - Centi Warspear<br>
<br>
My main problem is that in order to upgrade most of my slots - I would have to spend very high ammounts of platinum, often more than I can afford. My first instinct is to upgrade my greaves and BP to Acrylia, what would that go for? I rarely see it for sale on my server. I also want to avoid non-plate items, as I am a vain person :) (though I may settle on a barbed ringmail chestplate, which wouldn't look so bad if i wore it along with the rest of my plate items).<br>
<br>
The main stats I look for are AC, HP, MANA, Wis, Str and Sta, but I will not settle for filling a slot with an item with lower AC than I already have.<br>
<br>
I might also look into upgrading one of my 2 hander weapons, one of the velium lances would be nice - but would they be the best bet for my money?<br>
<br>
Thank you all for your input. <p><hr align="center" width="60%" size="1">
