<br>
1) Acrylia Plate BP.  AC 30, +5 Str, +15 Hp, +10 MR.  Should be ~3kpp.<br>
2) Acrylia Plate Greaves.  AC 20, +4 Agl, +10 Hp, +2 CR, +2 FR, +2 DR.  Should be ~2.5kpp.<br>
3) Crystal Chitin Vambraces.  AC 18, +5 Str, +5 Sta.  Should be ~3-4kpp.<br>
4) Bracer of Defence.  AC 15, +3 Sta.  Not sure on the price.<br>
<br>
